Package org.wikidata.wdtk.datamodel.json.jackson

Main package for Jackson-compatible implementations of the WDTK datamodel interfaces. The JSON serializations for snak values are different from the serializations used elsewhere (even when represented by the same WDTK interfaces), hence snak values have a seperate package.
Author:
Fredo Erxleben
